divs: Sighting DetailsSighting Report: I took pictures of ice on trees from a storm in late December 2004 at about 5:45 PM. I did not see anything at the time, but after the film was developed my wife noticed the objects high in the sky on the photo. Under examination with a magnifier the objects appear to be five spheres decending in size from left to right, the largest one being brownish in color in its entirety, while the other four are brown and white. These objects appear on the negative as well.
